						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone set up near the Basavaṇṇa temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 1130.</p>						

						<p>This inscription, dated in the <hi rend="bold">Chālukya-Vikrama year 55, Sādhāraṇa, Jyēshṭha ba. Pāḍiva, Monday,</hi> commemorates the death of <hi rend="bold">Bammaṇa,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Cheluvaya-Nāyaka.</hi> The hero died in a fight during a raid on <hi rend="bold">Mākanūr.</hi></p>						

						<p>The <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> corresponds to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1130, May, 25.</hi> The week-day however was <hi rend="bold">Sunday.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
